120
00:15:42,400 --> 00:15:55,710
i to je simptom najčešće kod Syphillnuma prvo, Sulph. drugi, Merc. to isto ima, 

121
00:15:55,810 --> 00:16:07,560
Pulsatilla to ima i naravno ARS., strah od patogenih, strah od prljavog.

122
00:16:20,060 --> 00:16:31,220
